      "body" : "I like the idea of automatically asking the user if it is ok to enable pruning in the event of insufficient disk space - however, I would prefer this feature waits until it's possible to turn off pruning without needing to re-download the entire block chain (i.e. only re-download the blocks that have been pruned).",
      "created_at" : "2016-10-19T05:38:34Z",
